[SN]TITLE[SN]
Hedgehogs might become extinct in Britain

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A new study has found that hedgehogs might soon be extinct in Britain.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
12 March 2016 Last updated at 08:22 GMT
It's thought that the number of hedgehogs decreases by five per cent each year.
Hayley's been looking at what one park in London is doing to help the prickly animals.
